<li><a href="http://finance-old.bi.no/~bernt/gcc_prog/recipes/recipes/node12.html" class="external text" title="http://finance-old.bi.no/~bernt/gcc_prog/recipes/recipes/node12.html" rel="nofollow">Option pricing by simulation</a>, Bernt Arne Ødegaard, <a href="/wiki/Norwegian_School_of_Management" title="Norwegian School of Management">Norwegian School of Management</a></li>
